data.description: Welcome to this meticulously maintained 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom single family attached townhome built in 2021.  Boasting a spacious 1552 square feet, this modern unit is filled with upgrades that are sure to impress.  The upstairs living space includes a spacious loft area which is ideal space awaiting your creativity for usage.  Luxury Wood-like EVP Flooring flows seamlessly throughout the downstairs, complemented by plush carpeting in standard areas with a 6 lb. Carpet Pad for added comfort.  The tile flooring in the laundry room and secondary bathrooms adds a touch of elegance, while the Primary Bath features a stunning tile floor and a Walk-In tile shower for a spa-like experience.  The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring white fantasy granite countertops and elemental, White cabinets with 42" upper cabinets, complete with crown molding and hardware.  The Dove White Cultured Marble Countertops in the Primary and Secondary Bathrooms offer both style and durability.  The Primary Bath also boasts a Double Vanity with Comfort Height Vanity, providing ample space for daily routines.  The property is equipped with top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, including a freestanding gas range, dishwasher, French door refrigerator, and microwave by Whirlpool.    Enjoy modern conveniences such as a Rinnai RL75i Tankless Water Heater, Kevo2 Bluetooth Deadbolt on the Front Entry, and a Liftmaster Wi-Fi Enabled Garage Door Opener.  The Deako Modular Light Switches with Two Smart Switches Included offer customizable lighting options, while two 110v/USB Combo Outlets in the Primary Bedroom and one on the Kitchen Island add practical functionality.   For laundry needs, a Whirlpool Top-Load High Efficiency Washer/Dryer Combo with a 4.3 cu. ft. washer and 7.0 cu.ft., electric dryer, equipped with AccuDry Sensor Drying System, are included for your convenience.  The plumbing fixtures by Moen Gibson in Chrome add a touch of sophistication to the space.    Living room windows and sliding glass door feature custom/cellular shades that not only enhance the aesthetic appeal of the townhome but also offer practical benefits, including energy efficiency and ease of use.  All bedroom windows are equipped with cordless faux wood blinds.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this upgraded and meticulously maintained townhome your new sanctuary.  Schedule a viewing today and experience the epitome of modern living.
